WEBVTT

00:04:29.519 --> 00:04:30.670
We changed policy.

00:04:30.694 --> 00:04:33.020
A consumer protection bill
that had been stalled

00:04:33.044 --> 00:04:35.167
in the Louisiana legislature for 10 years

00:04:35.191 --> 00:04:37.033
passed after we launched.

00:04:38.797 --> 00:04:39.948
Let's face it:

00:04:39.972 --> 00:04:42.367
this huge, slow-rolling
public health crisis

00:04:42.391 --> 00:04:44.258
is a national emergency.

00:04:44.649 --> 00:04:47.795
And I don't think government's
going to help us out anytime soon.

00:04:48.652 --> 00:04:50.800
But what if the answer was really simple:

00:04:50.824 --> 00:04:53.844
make all the prices public all the time.

00:04:54.605 --> 00:04:58.271
Would our individual bills go down?
Our health premiums?

00:04:59.749 --> 00:05:01.471
Be really clear about this: